data.description: Beautifully renovated turn of the century ranch duplex in downtown Indy! This has been touched head to toe from the brand new roof, down to the recently painted basement. Retaining the original character of the home, refinished hardwoods with high ceilings and original wood work remain. Kitchens and baths have all new cabinetry, granite counter tops, new ceramic tile, fixtures and lights. Stainless appliances finish out the kitchens. This home would be perfect for someone looking to have some rental income offset some of the mortgage . Property is 1 block from the new red line bus route, and just minutes from the Monon! This home has a ton of character and is move in ready!
